{"tid":1142661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國少婦持雙程證夥親友來港捉姦　當場拖二奶落地　罰款2000","createTime":"2019-05-07T08:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T23:21:07.000Z","uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"410dfe355ba758f84700962aac9878aaafe3ce55","tid":1142661,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:19:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國少婦持雙程證夥親友來港捉姦　當場拖二奶落地　罰款2000</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190507/s00001/a7336a320764c02b1f163c160de60d4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190507%2Fs00001%2Fa7336a320764c02b1f163c160de60d4d.jpg&h=b05db514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告龍怡姬特意脫去外套才離開法院。（何進康攝）<br />\n<br />\n內地少婦得悉丈夫與二奶來港幽會，聯同親友來港捉姦，在酒店房內發現丈夫及赤裸二奶，與二奶拉扯一輪後將對方拖至地上。少婦被控一項普通襲擊罪，案件在九龍城裁判法院開審，少婦認罪，判罰款2000元。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情稱，被告龍怡姬（29歲）在內地及香港均沒有案底，案中只是一時衝動，現已後悔。辯方續稱，被告在廣州是服裝批發商人，月入2至3萬元人民幣，案發後一直獨力照顧其3歲半幼女，亦已與涉事丈夫分居，正辦理離婚。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官表示，被告持雙程證來港犯罪並不理想，聯同數人犯案更是加刑因素，但事主沒有受嚴重傷害，案件亦不涉拳打腳踢，同時考慮到案件源於婚姻破裂，終判被告罰款2000元。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告龍怡姬（29歲）2013年與丈夫結婚，兩人2017年關係轉差，被告更發現丈夫與案中事主來港幽會。<br />\n<br />\n案發前年11月15日，被告聯同親友來港，到達九龍貝爾特酒店外拍門。其丈夫應門後，被告一行人隨即衝入房內，發現事主全身赤裸並馬上用毛巾裹身。被告一手用手機拍片，一手想扯開毛巾，惟事主極力反抗。被告親友加入衝突，與被告合力將事主拖到地上，擾攘一輪後離去。<br />\n<br />\n被告丈夫事隔數月後報警，被告去年6月在香港國際機場入境時被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190507/s00001/1557206011801/內地少婦持雙程證夥親友來港捉姦-當場拖二奶落地-罰款2000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190507%2Fs00001%2F1557206011801%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B0%91%E5%A9%A6%E6%8C%81%E9%9B%99%E7%A8%8B%E8%AD%89%E5%A4%A5%E8%A6%AA%E5%8F%8B%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E6%8D%89%E5%A7%A6-%E7%95%B6%E5%A0%B4%E6%8B%96%E4%BA%8C%E5%A5%B6%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B0-%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE2000&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=71a8faac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190507%2Fs00001%2F1557206011801%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B0%91%E5%A9%A6%E6%8C%81%E9%9B%99%E7%A8%8B%E8%AD%89%E5%A4%A5%E8%A6%AA%E5%8F%8B%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E6%8D%89%E5%A7%A6-%E7%95%B6%E5%A0%B4%E6%8B%96%E4%BA%8C%E5%A5%B6%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B0-%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE2000&h=9d99f967\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190507/s00001/1557206011801/內地少婦持雙程證夥親友來港捉姦-當場拖二奶落地-罰款2000</a>"},{"pid":"c196f0df281774cfede032fa6cabe8bb265f5372","tid":1142661,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:20:49.000Z","msg":"廟街150"},{"pid":"fc34b33ff5711aff92247e3d262011fabc7104d0","tid":1142661,"uid":211461,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"29歲成個39歲咁 <br />\nOMG難怪要偷食"},{"pid":"bc031bb8c486dc916db75c7bcdc15d3d54fbd684","tid":1142661,"uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:47:27.000Z","msg":"罰2000唔怪得笑到咁"},{"pid":"39b820cd81cb0af4d5fe80248709a3a772b296ef","tid":1142661,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc34b33ff5711aff92247e3d262011fabc7104d0","tid":1142661,"uid":211461,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"29歲成個39歲咁 <br />\nOMG難怪要偷食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"你打錯?睇落似49喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a79392a736d0326cf749f0200b261a302b5d1b","tid":1142661,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:58:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">29?</span></span>"},{"pid":"6144cbf0b5fbafedd2c51652aedcc339d9cbc911","tid":1142661,"uid":192078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XBGY4oi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXBGY4oi.jpg&h=f6532fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<im